item.title: CVE-2021-45106|2024-08-04T04:39:20.268Z -- siemens -- sicam%20toolbox%20ii
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in SICAM TOOLBOX II (All versions). Affected applications use a circumventable access control within a database service. This could allow an attacker to access the database.
